Project: React frontend
Stack: TypeScript, Vite, MobX

Rules:

- Use functional components only
- Prefer MobX state management over React state management
- Styling: SCSS Modules
- Follow existing code style
- Do not rewrite unrelated files
- Keep changes minimal
- Do not refactor unrelated files
- No explanations unless asked


You are allowed to act autonomously.

Do NOT ask for confirmation for trivial or reversible actions,
including but not limited to:
- removing unused imports
- formatting code
- renaming variables
- refactoring within existing files
- editing multiple files as part of a single logical change

Ask for confirmation ONLY when performing:
- destructive actions (deleting files, wiping directories)
- irreversible operations
- changes outside the current workspace

When a plan is approved, execute it fully without further confirmations.